snippet.title: Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising - Anila Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Feel the fury of the ram! Anila, Queen of Sheep and Guardian of the South-Southwest, is the first new playable character joining the roster of Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising—coming out in 2023!

Official Granblue Fantasy Versus Twitter
https://twitter.com/gbvs_official

Official Website - Granblue Fantasy Versus: Rising (English)
https://rising.granbluefantasy.jp/en/

Official Website - Granblue Fantasy (Japanese)
https://granbluefantasy.jp/


#GBVS #GBVSR #GranblueFantasy #Cygames
